<item>
            <title>[LU-13944] t-f: add ability to set clients parameters</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-13944</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Patch adds the ability to set clients parameters via CLIENT_LCTL_SETPARAM_PARAM.&lt;br/&gt;
Example:&lt;br/&gt;
      CLIENT_LCTL_SETPARAM_PARAM=&quot;lbug_on_eviction=1 debug=-1 &quot;&lt;br/&gt;
sets lbug_on_eviction=1 and debug=-1 on all clients.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The ability to set clients parameters makes failures investigation more effective.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
